Text: Hi! For Melissa’s birthday I’m making a video compilation of everyone singing happy birthday to Melissa and I’ll edit it all into on happy birthday music video. I’m asking everyone to record themselves singing happy birthday and to please send to me. Do you think you could records yourselves singing happy birthday and send it to me by tomorrow evening?
To clarify…a video recording, not audio
